dct_title_s: Τοπογραφικός χάρτης Προύσης και των περιξ.
dct_description_sm:
Relief shown by hachures. Map shows settlements, roads, bridges, and camping sites. Gift of the Program in Hellenic Studies with the support of the Stanley J. Seeger Hellenic Fund. Relief shown by hachures.
Roads, bridges, and built areas of settlements are shown. Issued in: Hē Prousa: ētoi, archaiologikē, historikē, geōgraphikē kai ekklēsiastikē perigraphē autēs met' episynēmmenōn archaiōn epigraphōn topographikou chartou kai eikonōn diaphorōn oikodomēmatōn.
dct_publisher_sm: Athēnai : Typographeion ho Asmodaios G. Staurianou, 1883.
